          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How can I figure out the correct size for me?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Each item you select will have a 'Size Chart' on the product page. You can refer to the size chart and the provided sketch on 'How to Measure' to determine the right size of shoes. You can also visit our <a href=\"https://fitflopindia.myshopify.com/pages/find-your-fit\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://fitflopindia.myshopify.com/pages/find-your-fit\"><strong>Find Your Fit</strong></a> page to find your accurate size.</p>",
